    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 7.68,
      "text": "Google just dropped Disco, their new AI browser that basically combines googling with vibe coding. And it works by using a new feature called GenTabs.",
      "confidence": 0.9550733
    },
    {
      "start": 7.7599998,
      "end": 20.765,
      "text": "It basically scans all your open browser tabs, then spots patterns in your browsing, and instantly turns them into task specific custom mini apps. So instead of switch switching between 20 different pages, Disco scans them all and then builds you a single interactive dashboard.",
      "confidence": 0.96268785
    },
    {
      "start": 20.925,
      "end": 27.005001,
      "text": "For example, if you ask for travel tips, it'll create a full trip planner app with interactive maps and hotel price comparisons.",
      "confidence": 0.98873466
    },
    {
      "start": 27.165,
